      get rid of h... I mean, he found a better opportunity.
    - Anyway, I'm Pig Boss. I'll teach you the basics.
    - First, learn to move the camera.
    - Drag with your finger to pan around, then use the zoom buttons to zoom in and
      out.
    completionMessages:
    - Good. Now you can move around.
